# Yomitan -> Anki field mapping for ModernZ sentence mining
# Deck: Anime::Mining
# Model: ModernZ Mining Sentence
#
# Configure in Yomitan:
#   Settings -> Anki -> Enable Anki integration
#   -> Configure Anki card format -> Terms tab
#   -> Deck: Anime::Mining, Model: ModernZ Mining Sentence

Anki field          | Yomitan marker                              | Notes
--------------------|---------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------
VocabKanji          | {expression}                                | Optional target word on the back
VocabDef            | {glossary-brief}                            | Optional definition on the back
SentKanji           | {cloze-prefix}{cloze-body}{cloze-suffix}    | Sentence context; front stays sentence-first
VocabPitchPattern   | {pitch-accents}                             | Optional
VocabPitchNum       | {pitch-accent-positions}                    | Optional
VocabFurigana       | (leave empty)                               | AJT Japanese fills after note creation
SentFurigana        | (leave empty)                               | AJT Japanese fills after note creation
SentEng             | (leave empty)                               | Filled by mpvacious from English secondary subs
SentAudio           | (leave empty)                               | Filled by mpvacious from anime audio
Image               | (leave empty)                               | Filled by mpvacious from the scene screenshot
VocabAudio          | (leave empty)                               | Optional
Notes               | (leave empty)                               | Optional
